text: The 1965 Navy Midshipmen football team represented the United States Naval Academy (USNA) during the 1965 NCAA University Division football season. Navy competed as an independent with no conference affiliation. The team was led by first-year head coach Bill Elias. ==Schedule== ==Personnel== ==References== Navy Midshipmen Category:Navy Midshipmen football seasons Navy Midshipmen
